data.name: Term counts

data.name: Capabilities
data.description: This tool will reset the admin, customer and shop_manager roles to default. Use this if your users cannot access all of the WooCommerce admin pages.

data.name: Clear customer sessions
data.description: Note: This tool will delete all customer session data from the database, including current carts and saved carts in the database.

data.name: Clear template cache
data.description: Note: This tool will empty the template cache.

data.name: Create default WooCommerce pages
data.description: Note: This tool will install all the missing WooCommerce pages. Pages already defined and set up will not be replaced.

data.name: Delete WooCommerce tax rates
data.description: Note: This option will delete ALL of your tax rates, use with caution. This action cannot be reversed.

data.name: Update database
data.description: Note: This tool will update your WooCommerce database to the latest version. Please ensure you make sufficient backups before proceeding.

data.name: Verify base database tables
data.description: Verify if all base database tables are present.

data.name: Regenerate the product attributes lookup table
data.description: This tool will regenerate the product attributes lookup table data from existing product(s) data. This process may take a while.

data.name: Clear analytics cache
data.description: This tool will reset the cached values used in WooCommerce Analytics. If numbers still look off, try Reimporting Historical Data.
